{"id": 1032, "genre": 1001, "title": "你在生活中都遇到过哪些不走心？", "description": "一种形式主义，而且不精致。（题图来自：FLAVIO MORAIS）", "record_count": 2443, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201607031813492CJM04iLVbcyHNUI.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-06-25T01:00:16Z", "options": [{"id": 92672, "content": "走心朋友少的可怜?", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 656978}, {"id": 92673, "content": "我的二级证或许被辅导班遗忘在哪个角落了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 656978}, {"id": 92930, "content": "把我名字的麒念成麟", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 635729}, {"id": 92675, "content": "我想跟你说个事儿，呃，算了吧……（艹）", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 656986}, {"id": 97795, "content": "男票等你试衣服，看都不看说：好看！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 152720}, {"id": 92676, "content": "我想跟你说个事儿，呃，算了吧……（艹）", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 656986}, {"id": 92932, "content": "生活需要热情", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182859b4pV1drXfews6AEF.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 657719}, {"id": 92677, "content": "test", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 486965}, {"id": 93190, "content": "喝汤的时候勺子伸到鼻子前", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 657975}, {"id": 92679, "content": "学校每次搞活动，太阳那个火辣辣啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 656961}, {"id": 93960, "content": "送礼物直接送钱，美其名曰：你喜欢什么就自己买什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 493373}, {"id": 92937, "content": "朋友圈不看图就点赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 541445}, {"id": 92682, "content": "新闻联播", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 653430}, {"id": 93195, "content": "升国旗的时候永远都看旗子是不是跟着节奏到顶?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 638540}, {"id": 93196, "content": "升国旗的时候看旗子是不是跟着节奏到顶", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 638540}, {"id": 93708, "content": "每次点菜都说随便，然后点完了就说怎么点这个? ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 660793}, {"id": 104204, "content": "晚安", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700756}, {"id": 92942, "content": "早上我妈问吃鸡蛋么？\n然而我已连续20年空腹吃鸡蛋胃疼死了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 656377}, {"id": 93198, "content": "在专注想一件事情的时候，其他做的说的都是不走心的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 658340}, {"id": 93710, "content": "每一条都点赞?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 660793}, {"id": 92431, "content": "什么事儿你都给我点个赞！", "image": null, "praise_count": 491, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 569682}, {"id": 92432, "content": "出门反复确认还是忘带钥匙……", "image": null, "praise_count": 53, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 640827}, {"id": 92688, "content": "微信的迷之微笑", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 624708}, {"id": 92433, "content": "感情深一口闷！                                                呵呵，谁特么跟你感情深?", "image": null, "praise_count": 256, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 419840}, {"id": 92434, "content": "男朋友不走心的说：行行行 是我错了 行了吧？———呵呵 哪能是你错了啊 明明是我无情是我无义是我无理取闹呢～", "image": "img/option/option/20160703152239h2s9akZewtpXQ7HI.jpg", "praise_count": 232, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274056}, {"id": 92946, "content": "眼镜压坏了，将就着戴几天吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 657737}, {"id": 92435, "content": "点赞！！！！！！！！！不是很懂这个功能", "image": null, "praise_count": 68, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 612588}, {"id": 92436, "content": "上课？", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 458087}, {"id": 93204, "content": "你真心待人，而她只认为是场交易", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 565066}, {"id": 92437, "content": "好好好", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 116772}, {"id": 92438, "content": "祝福短信落款都不是本人", "image": null, "praise_count": 142, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155086}, {"id": 92439, "content": "收纳好的东西绝对找不到。我不要再整理了。我不扫天下了。我放弃。", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 253261}, {"id": 92440, "content": "卫生巾贴歪了不整 别赞要脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 172, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 435247}, {"id": 92696, "content": "“你结婚了？”，“嗯”，“恭喜你”", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 657020}, {"id": 92441, "content": "纠结穿哪件衣服问男朋友意见，打游戏的他头也不抬说：你穿哪件都好看", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 542160}, {"id": 92442, "content": "学校的宣传栏和各种海报！", "image": null, "praise_count": 63, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 330854}, {"id": 93210, "content": "自己特想做的事表现得很明显了，非问人家你想不想，你要不要～～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 607950}, {"id": 92443, "content": "哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 495586}, {"id": 92699, "content": "介绍的时候叫错名", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 199459}, {"id": 92700, "content": "你想吃什么？\n我想吃……！！！\n，……嗯，还是吃这个吧！?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 656060}, {"id": 92445, "content": "好多人的脸长得都不走心 ，比如我！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 481152}, {"id": 92703, "content": "人与人之间的信任建立在什么之上？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 620393}, {"id": 92448, "content": "和舍友开黑，明明自己的锅，却要甩给她。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 534936}, {"id": 92449, "content": "多喝点热水", "image": null, "praise_count": 43, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 655421}, {"id": 92705, "content": "学校门口礼物店的礼物", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 641796}, {"id": 92962, "content": "在干嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 333732}, {"id": 92452, "content": "吃什么？随便", "image": null, "praise_count": 156, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 623377}, {"id": 92454, "content": "我好像很久少走心", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 563266}, {"id": 92966, "content": "约好九点，十一点才到，相机没有充电，回去拿充电器再等一小时。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 550293}, {"id": 93478, "content": "欧洲杯这么久，问朋友，怎么没见巴西？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 650086}]}